title: Exercise Crossed Swords 2025
description: The exercise Crossed Swords 2025  brought together 240 participants from around 40 nations, including both NATO and partner nations. The comprehensive cyber defence exercise trains cyber defenders to carry out both defensive and full-spectrum offensive cyber operations within a simulated crisis and conflict environment.

title: Locked Shields 2025
description: Locked Shields is the world's largest and most complex cyber defence exercise, which provides the most realistic and future oriented training environment for the cyber defenders of NATO and partners. It is organised in cooperation with the leading experts from cyber industry, academia and allied cyber defence forces.

title: Reverse Engineering 101: How to Dissect and Master Any Platform
description: Ever wanted to be a Reverse Engineer?  Don't know where to start?
